      "content": "thanks, that's a good start. to make my rebuttal stronger, i need to really understand the \"scientific\" part you mentioned. can you expand on those risk assessment arguments? like, how did they specifically argue that certain racial or ethnic demographics were a \"risk\" to property values or economic stability? i need the specific logic they used to connect race to financial risk so i can deconstruct it in the debate.",
